premise_source_doc_sentence: Liberty Lettice Lark Ross  (  born 23 September 1978  )  is an English model and actress .
She has appeared in publications such as Vogue , Harper 's Bazaar , i-D , and Dazed & Confused .
She played the role of Queen Eleanor in the 2012 fantasy film Snow White and the Huntsman , directed by her then-husband , Rupert Sanders .
She is the sister of composers Atticus and Leopold Ross .
